-- Hungary Budget Improves ‘Sustainably,’ Hahn Tells Magyar Nemzet
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-06-07T06:12:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/hungary-budget-improves-sustainably-hahn-tells-magyar-nemzet.html
Hungary’s plans to keep the budget
deficit below European Union limits are “respectable” as they
improve the balance “sustainably in the long term,” Johannes Hahn, the EU commissioner for regional policy, told  Magyar
Nemzet .  To contact the reporter on this story:
